snippet.textDisplay:
Maine kisi interview  me suna tha ki Lata Maa hamesha  geet ki dairy samne rkh k gaati  thi.

Aaj ye smjh me aaya ki wo aisa kyu koti thi.

Kyoki bhaaw me aakr koi shbd galt n ho.jaae.

Aapse antre me ye galti ho gyi
*Aansuon ke Dard se* hogya pahle fir aapne sudhar kr ke *aanshuwo se Dard ke* kar diya.

Baaki sb to kamal ka hi hai.
No comparison  with original but its also a good one.
Always love Sunidhi mam's voice and versatility.
